Introduction

Leader'S G (Korean: 리더스 G) was a sub-unit of Leader'S. the frequent line-up changes of the main group lead to the merging of their sub-unit's, Leader'S G was the first unit to dissolve, with the remaining members of the unit being moved to Leader'S N. The sub-unit was created in October 2011, after TGN Entertainment announced that they plan to reorganize the group, in order to have twenty-four members.
